{"tid":803770,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股票就好似拍拖咁","createTime":"2018-09-02T13:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T09:50:32.000Z","uid":147160,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5d145d24a9a629ffcfeb77f9cb4a3af7633285","tid":803770,"uid":147160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"9up下股經先<br />\n爛股好似愛情騙子咁,經常甜言蜜語,編出各種動聽故事使投資者入市,每次投資者都失望而回,最後分手離場,而愈遲退出者就會傷痕愈深,痛苦愈大。分手後,愛情騙子又會搵個第二個對象,按股市周期,循環不息。自覺高手玩家如果係都要同愛子騙子交往,最多只可以發展極期短線的愛情,絕不可交心, 唔係曬時間又曬精力。如果你認為自己無限金錢,請隨便吧~ 打完之後我諗起美容雞,爛股全部都係雞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c2129abfb3bda9fd3dee6251aafb7fbfa08ea9","tid":803770,"uid":47466,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"全部股票都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cfdae1f7a86bb9a88be75b1e694dced58d693f","tid":803770,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T14:26:03.000Z","msg":"未入就陣就不停咁升，入左就暴跌"},{"pid":"2538be900bfca11ae0a445a05ebe8049ea006151","tid":803770,"uid":147160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55cfdae1f7a86bb9a88be75b1e694dced58d693f","tid":803770,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T14:26:03.000Z","msg":"未入就陣就不停咁升，入左就暴跌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T22:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心同感受 成日比個市呃"},{"pid":"9f264f16d70f16b315bc246025c0d32bdd7cfb8b","tid":803770,"uid":117947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T23:15:24.000Z","msg":"男人